23
00:02:10,249 --> 00:02:11,217
"Simono"

24
00:02:11,217 --> 00:02:12,284
"Simono"
You're late!

25
00:02:12,284 --> 00:02:14,286
"Simono"
Are you trying to starve me to death?!

26
00:02:14,286 --> 00:02:16,914
"Simono"
I'm sorry! I'll make your
breakfast right away!

27
00:02:21,393 --> 00:02:24,096
This tastes bad. Make it over again.

28
00:02:24,096 --> 00:02:26,929
But I'll be late to school, so...

29
00:02:28,467 --> 00:02:31,265
Don't you care what happens to them?!

30
00:02:32,671 --> 00:02:35,107
Yukky! Pinky!

31
00:02:35,107 --> 00:02:38,099
I could kill them at any time!

32
00:02:39,869 --> 00:02:44,903
"Bound Girl"

33
00:02:54,313 --> 00:02:56,548
I see that girl around a lot lately.

34
00:02:56,548 --> 00:02:58,450
I wonder if she moved
into the neighborhood.

35
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:00,252
It's nothing like that!

36
00:03:00,252 --> 00:03:03,983
I heard she lives in the
big condo next to the park.

37
00:03:05,491 --> 00:03:08,994
She apparently goes to
Ms. Simono's place for tutoring

38
00:03:08,994 --> 00:03:12,631
and the girl cooks for her
in return. Every day!

39
00:03:12,631 --> 00:03:13,732
What?!

40
00:03:13,732 --> 00:03:16,602
Is Ms. Simono even capable of tutoring?!

41
00:03:16,602 --> 00:03:18,771
She hates children, doesn't she?

42
00:03:18,771 --> 00:03:22,374
But she used to be a
school teacher, you know.

43
00:03:22,374 --> 00:03:25,778
Though, she quit immediately when
she inherited her parents' fortune.

44
00:03:25,778 --> 00:03:28,113
I wonder if her parents are aware of this.

45
00:03:28,113 --> 00:03:28,447
"Curry"

46
00:03:28,447 --> 00:03:30,816
"Curry"
They apparently came
to meet her once, but...

47
00:03:30,816 --> 00:03:32,785
"Curry"
