and actual names are entirely coincidental."

368
00:24:31,172 --> 00:24:33,107
Your name?

369
00:24:33,107 --> 00:24:35,509
Inori Ujiie.

370
00:24:35,509 --> 00:24:38,379
You are not happy?

371
00:24:38,379 --> 00:24:42,917
I have no kin, and yet,
she welcomed me into her family.

372
00:24:42,917 --> 00:24:44,251
I was so happy.

373
00:24:44,251 --> 00:24:48,222
I wanted to repay her kindness, but...

374
00:24:48,222 --> 00:24:50,291
Your wish?

375
00:24:50,291 --> 00:24:52,960
Banish her to Hell for me!

376
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:55,863
Your grievance has been heard.

